1. Old Kent Road — Price: $60, Rent: $2
2. Chance
3. Whitechapel Road — Price: $60, Rent: $4
4. Income Tax — Pay $100 to Free Parking pot
5. Jail / Just Visiting
6. The Angel Islington — Price: $100, Rent: $6
7. Free Parking
8. Euston Road — Price: $100, Rent: $6
9. Chance
